हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://kukufm.com/show/rosy-psycho/?utm_source=share_sh
show.description: Born into luxury and raised with limitless affection, Gigi Philips radiates warmth and kindness in everything she does. As the sole heir to cosmetic empire ROSE Beauty and Cosmetics, controlled by her powerful parents James and Laura Philips, she's being groomed to eventually take the reins of the family business. But beneath the glamorous facade of board meetings and billion-dollar decisions lies a young woman whose genuine sweetness might be her greatest strength—or her biggest liability—in the cutthroat world of corporate beauty. Follow Gigi's journey as she navigates the complexities of wealth, power, and finding her own voice in a world that expects nothing less than perfection.
